import {sample} from './'

export default function generateBalloonColour() {
  const colours = [
    "#db504a",
    "#ff6f59",
    "#ffe200",
    "#9bf6ff",
    '#ffd6a5',
    '#caffbf',
    '#ffc6ff',
    '#bdb2ff',
    '#e9ff70',
    '#ff70a6',
    '#ff9770'
  ]
  return sample(colours)
}
